Crossbow<br/>
<br/>
Average Length: 3.5 to 4 feet.<br/>
<br/>
Type of Weapon: Missle Weapon.<br/>
<br/>
Commonly used by: Crossbowmen.<br/>
<br/>
These weapons were often used on castle walls, as they had tremendous range<br/>
and power. They were slower to reload than Long Bows, and therefore were not<br/>
often used in army-to-army combat, but they were fantastic in defending<br/>
against sieges.<br/>
